msgstr "Ursprunget"

#: .\electricity\templates\electricity\about.html:126
msgid ""
"We started with a simple question: In a world of fast fixes, who is looking "
"out for the next twenty years?"
msgstr ""
"We started with a simple question: In a world of fast fixes, who is looking "
"out for the next twenty years?"

#: .\electricity\templates\electricity\about.html:130
msgid ""
"RWM EL was founded on the belief that technical skill is only half of the "
"job. The other half is the integrity to do things right when no one is "
"watching. In the Swedish electrical landscape, precision isn't an option—"
"it's the foundation of every safe home."
msgstr ""
"RWM EL was founded on the belief that technical skill is only half of the "
"job. The other half is the integrity to do things right when no one is "
"watching. In the Swedish electrical landscape, precision isn't an option—"
"it's the foundation of every safe home."

#: .\electricity\templates\electricity\about.html:140
msgid "What RWM EL Stands For"
msgstr "Vad RWM EL står för"

#: .\electricity\templates\electricity\about.html:142
msgid ""
"We stand for the quiet confidence that comes from knowing your "
"infrastructure is handled by professionals who respect the craft. Our "
"approach is methodical, Scandinavian in its simplicity, and uncompromising "
"in its execution."
msgstr ""
"We stand for the quiet confidence that comes from knowing your "
"infrastructure is handled by professionals who respect the craft. Our "
"approach is methodical, Scandinavian in its simplicity, and uncompromising "
"in its execution."

#: .\electricity\templates\electricity\about.html:143
msgid ""
"Every wire we pull and every panel we install is a testament to our "
"commitment to Swedish engineering excellence and local safety regulations."
msgstr ""
"Every wire we pull and every panel we install is a testament to our "
"commitment to Swedish engineering excellence and local safety regulations."

#: .\electricity\templates\electricity\about.html:148
msgid ""
"Electrical work is regulated in Sweden because incorrect installations are "
"dangerous. We don't just follow the law; we champion the safety it provides."
msgstr ""
"Electrical work is regulated in Sweden because incorrect installations are "
"dangerous. We don't just follow the law; we champion the safety it provides."

#: .\electricity\templates\electricity\about.html:160
msgid "Why We Do This"
msgstr "Varför vi gör detta"

#: .\electricity\templates\electricity\about.html:164
msgid ""
"We do this because a home should be a sanctuary, not a source of technical "
"anxiety. We do this because we believe in the longevity of quality. When we "
"leave a site, we leave behind more than just working lights—we leave behind "
"the peace of mind that your family or business is protected by a system "
"designed to endure."
msgstr ""
"We do this because a home should be a sanctuary, not a source of technical "
"anxiety. We do this because we believe in the longevity of quality. When we "
"leave a site, we leave behind more than just working lights—we leave behind "
"the peace of mind that your family or business is protected by a system "
"designed to endure."

